metadata.name: DAO HOUSE FRIENDS #1
metadata.description: DAO House Friends PFP is a collection of digital art, first and foremost, with the added benefits of utility. We have partnered with a well established Web2 artist to launch their first NFT. This unique, digitally native artwork will offer owners digital access to the DAO House community, exclusive collaborations with creators, future drops, and a piece of NFT art history.
